"\n"
"The key insight: §0 where §1 is *definitionally equal* to §2. The\n"
"§3 tactic swaps between these two views. You did not need any\n"
"special set theory — just §4 to see through the notation, and then\n"
"§5 for the arithmetic.\n"
"\n"
"**Recipe**: To prove §6, use §7 to reveal the\n"
